variable.description: WERE CONTACT LENSES WORN DURING VISION EXAM?
variable.comment: PARTICIPANTS WERE ASKED TO REMOVE THEIR EYEGLASSES BEFORE THE REFRACTION READINGS WERE TAKEN. RECOMMEND EXCLUDING DATA FOR A GIVEN EYE IF CONTACT LENSES WERE WORN. . EXCLUDE LEFT EYE DATA IF LENSSTAT2=1 or 2 or 3 or 5 or 6. (IN OTHER WORDS, ONLY INCLUDE IF LENSSTAT2= 0 or 4 or 7) EXCLUDE RIGHT EYE DATA IF LENSTAT2=1 or 2 or 4 or 5 or 6.
